    <h1 class="header"> <span class="itemprop" itemprop="name">François Ozon</span> 
        
        
    </h1>
    
        <div class="infobar" id="name-job-categories">
            
            
<a href="#director"
onclick="nameJobCategoriesClickHandler(this)" > <span class="itemprop" itemprop="jobTitle">
Director</span></a>                 <span class="ghost">|</span> 
            
            
<a href="#writer"
onclick="nameJobCategoriesClickHandler(this)" > <span class="itemprop" itemprop="jobTitle">
Writer</span></a>                 <span class="ghost">|</span> 
            
            
<a href="#editor"
onclick="nameJobCategoriesClickHandler(this)" > <span class="itemprop" itemprop="jobTitle">
Editor</span></a>            
        </div>
    
        <hr/>
                        
<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
François Ozon was born on November 15, 1967 in Paris, France. He is a director and writer, known for <a href="/title/tt0324133?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">Swimming Pool</a> (2003), <a href="/title/tt0283832?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">8 femmes</a> (2002) and <a href="/title/tt1964624?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">Dans la maison</a> (2012).            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0654830/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
    <div id="name-born-info" class="txt-block">
        <h4 class="inline">Born:</h4> 
   
  <time datetime="1967-11-15" itemprop="birthDate">
<a href="/search/name?birth_monthday=11-15&refine=birth_monthday&ref_=nm_ov_bth_monthday"
>November 15</a>, 
     
<a href="/search/name?birth_year=1967&ref_=nm_ov_bth_year"
>1967</a>    
  </time>
            in
            <a href="/search/name?birth_place=Paris,+France&ref_=nm_ov_bth_place"
>Paris, France</a>
    </div>

                        
                        
                   </td>
