    <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
        <div id="dyk-personal-quote" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Personal Quote:</h4>
I think I'm more lucid portraying women because I don't have the feeling it's about me. Of course it's about me and my emotions, but it's not like when I'm in front of the male character I have to be, in front of a mirror. With the man, I try maybe to hide some personal things. And with a woman, because I am a man it's easier. It's strange, but it's like that.                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0654830/bio?ref_=nm_dyk_qt_sm#quotes"
>See more</a> 
                    </span>
                    &raquo;
        </div>
            <hr/>
        <div id="dyk-trivia" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Trivia:</h4>
Calls actress <a href="/name/nm0304801?ref_=nm_dyk_trv1">Romola Garai</a> his muse.                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0654830/bio?ref_=nm_dyk_trv_sm#trivia"
>See more</a>
                    </span>
